    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事概述</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场灾难性事件将曾经美丽而骄傲的希腊罗马太空船阿特罗米托斯，变成了来自未知维度的恐怖生物滋生的温床。事后，一股神秘力量选择介入命运，从瓦砾与灰烬中将阿德斯忒亚唤醒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为阿德斯忒亚，你的使命是阻止你的孪生妹妹哈耳摩尼亚毁灭宇宙，但仍有诸多问题未解。在寻找答案的过程中，你探索这艘庞大的太空船，同时获得可能塑造你最终命运的力量、知识与技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一款以掌握杂技般的自由战斗为核心的类银河战士恶魔城游戏。探索一个融合多元玩法风格的环境，满足每位玩家的需求。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>令人叹为观止的环境</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心打造各具特色的区域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/19e53537abb20910cff6022317d0c6c3.poster.avif?t=1766135484\" width=780 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/19e53537abb20910cff6022317d0c6c3.webm?t=1766135484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/19e53537abb20910cff6022317d0c6c3.mp4?t=1766135484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>显现以太灯笼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以太灯笼是阿德斯忒亚的核心移动能力。通过变形为一颗璀璨的太阳般星辰来挑战重力，随心所欲地向任何方向释放能量。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>额外的灯笼可实现连续冲刺，即使在半空中也能一个接一个地使用</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/3975cf66f1163ddfcd5b97ec61bd2360.poster.avif?t=1766135484\" width=780 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/3975cf66f1163ddfcd5b97ec61bd2360.webm?t=1766135484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299290/extras/3975cf66f1163ddfcd5b97ec61bd2360.mp4?t=1766135484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\